	<tr>
		<td colspan="2"><hr class="sep" />Use the EXT pins to look for the values 0, 4, 8, and C, and use it to drive a multiplexer that selects between the video_out pins of 2 PPUs.<br /><br />Hypothetically, this would yield 2 video planes with 2 independent palettes, and sprites of the low plane would have their own colors as well.

		

		</td>
	</tr>
	</table>


